In my case, linux-2.2.0-pre1-ac4, FAT/VFAT/nls is modules, IDE disk compiled
in, all using kmod. VFAT partition was created by Win95 OSR2, but now
running win98. I have one single 8.4gb hdd, two vfat partitions of 3.0 and
3.1 GB. Using egcs 1.1.1 release, binutils-2.9.1.0.19a.
